im sorry to say that the keygen is a virus.. however if you have an up to date antivirius it shouldnt be a problem. just use this key instead.
5000-0000000-0000000-5068
just ignore your antivirius' concerns for a restart and just mount the first disc, enter the key and begin the install. (i recommend virtual clone drive - its a small dl, simple and its free) 
mount the 2nd disc when promompted and continue the install process. once completed,
right click the 1st disc and click explore.(the virtual drives are found under Computer for all you N00bs) 
go to cd key + keygen.... and copy the crack file 
(once again just heal the virius and click no to a restart) paste the zip file somewhere and extract it. now drop that file into the install directory (c/program files/ea games/ wateva) and replace the original exe with the crack. create shortcut from this new exe and drop it on the desktop or whatever.

if this virus thing bothers you, you could always remove the keygen by unloading it into a program like magic iso, deleting the keygen, then repacking it back into an ISO.
